
## Position Display Logic

The app uses color-coded position classes:

| Position | Class | Color |
|----------|-------|-------|
| #1 | `pos-1` | Green (top rank) |
| #2-3 | `pos-3` | Light green |
| #4-10 | `pos-10` | Yellow |
| #11-20 | `pos-20` | Orange |
| Not Found | `pos-nf` | Red |

## In Short

A local SEO tool for tracking and analyzing Google Business Profile search rankings over time.
